snippet.title: Best VGM 665 - Metroid Prime Hunters - Deep Arcterra
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Metroid Prime Hunters (2006)
Deep Arcterra
Lawrence Schwedler, James Phillipsen & Kenji Yamamoto
